If you want to start to change your own behavior.

9
00:00:37,180 --> 00:00:42,070
It is very important to first to understand the concept of willpower.

10
00:00:42,070 --> 00:00:45,340
Research has established that willpower behaves as a muscle:

11
00:00:45,340 --> 00:00:49,750
if you use your willpower you exhaust your muscle of willpower.

12
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:57,480
Or to frame it differently you can see willpower as a sort of reservoir of self-control.

13
00:00:57,480 --> 00:01:05,449
Every time you do something that requires willpower or self control you deplete the

14
00:01:05,449 --> 00:01:06,430
reservoir.

15
00:01:06,430 --> 00:01:12,300
If it’s a reservoir with a limited amount of willpower or self-control,

16
