I can imagine that you want to apply it in the best possible way,

17
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,979
to get the best outcome out of it.

18
00:01:17,979 --> 00:01:20,530
How do we do it?

19
00:01:20,530 --> 00:01:25,500
The best way to change you behavior, given this concept of willpower,

20
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:30,040
is by creating new habits or new rituals.

21
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:34,030
A habit or ritual is an action that you do automatically,

22
00:01:34,030 --> 00:01:38,490
therefore it does not require any willpower or self-control,

23
00:01:38,490 --> 00:01:40,220
you just do it without thinking.

24
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:43,549
Luckily, there is a lots of research available on how

25
