people can change their habits or rituals.

26
00:01:48,970 --> 00:01:52,720
Tony Schwarz has made a very useful checklist for this.

27
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:58,369
Let me illustrate this checklist with a personal example of a situation in which I was able

28
00:01:58,369 --> 00:02:03,090
to change my behavior.

29
00:02:03,090 --> 00:02:07,590
I had some back problems and therefore I had to work less.

30
00:02:07,590 --> 00:02:20,819
The first  check was about creating an ambition that is on the one hand very realistic but on the

31
00:02:20,819 --> 00:02:25,909
other hand it is also motivating enough to get you exited.

32
00:02:25,909 --> 00:02:29,109
What I decided up on was to finish every day at six.

33
00:02:29,109 --> 00:02:33,409
This was realistic as well as motivating.

34
00:02:33,409 --> 00:02:42,919
The  second check is about how you define it.

35
00:02:42,919 --> 00:02:45,799
It should be very precise and very specific.

36
00:02:45,799 --> 00:02:51,650
In my case finishing every day at 6 is neither really precise nor specific.

37
00:02:51,650 --> 00:02:54,709
It more an outcome than actually doing something.

38
00:02:54,709 --> 00:03:00,120
Therefore I framed it as: “Start every day with those tasks that needed

39
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:07,879
to be get done that day, instead of doing something else”.

40
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:11,230
That is specific enough to get me going.

41
00:03:11,230 --> 00:03:17,749
So for instance not starting with fun email or going on Whatsapp?

42
00:03:17,749 --> 00:03:20,389
Start with the task at hand in the morning.

43
00:03:20,389 --> 00:03:20,980
Yes exactly.

44
00:03:20,980 --> 00:03:22,439
That is a good point.

45
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:26,469
That is also where to third check is about: You need to understand what are you going

46
00:03:26,469 --> 00:03:29,730
to resist, when you are implementing this habit.

47
00:03:29,730 --> 00:03:32,430
Because typically you already have some type of behavior.

48
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:35,849
You need to be conscious: What am I not going to do and what am I going

49
00:03:35,849 --> 00:03:37,930
to do instead.

50
00:03:37,930 --> 00:03:40,439
That is check number 3.

51
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:44,790
Number four is more about understanding what are other commitments that I made,

52
00:03:44,790 --> 00:03:50,069
